entries.title_d: An enemy patrol of Imperial TIE fighters have spotted you. Defeat them to complete the mission.
entries.title: Naboo system: Eliminate Enemy Patrol.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Command: < We have uploaded a new patrol route for you to check out pilot. Hopefully we will have more success this time. >
entries.complete: Rebel Command: < Mission Complete!  Return to base for your next assignment by travelling to the Naboo space station and using /comm. >
